-- Latvian Parliament Confirms New Government of Prime Minister Dombrovskis
-- B y   A a r o n   E g l i t i s
-- 2010-11-03T09:10:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-03/latvian-parliament-confirms-new-government-of-prime-minister-dombrovskis.html
Latvia’s parliament voted 63-35 to
confirm a two-party government led by Prime Minister Valdis
Dombrovskis a month after national elections increased the
government’s majority.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Aaron Eglitis in Riga at 
 aeglitis@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
